data.description: This beautiful 5 bedroom home has been largely updated and offers a tremendous value for any buyer in our market.   This house is full of character inside and out and was built thoughtfully on a large level lot.  The primary bedroom is on the main level along with mostly open concept living area into formal/informal dining, den and huge new kitchen. The upper level provides 4 generous sized bedrooms large enough for king-size bedroom suites.  This is a quiet established neighborhood in a very convenient location for access to most modern amenities. Please call us to schedule a private showing or with any questions!
